{
  "stem": "4361.7",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And I remember thinking, it's going to be now a different world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "All the bad that happened will never again be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "Now it's going to be truly a new world, a good world, a clean world, no prejudice-- freedom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I thought it's just going to be that way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "I mean, it was a plateau that is the more painful to remember because it was an illusion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "But that's what I thought.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And that I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end and the beginning of my idealism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right at the beginning-- I mean, the height of my idealism, not the end, the height of my believing in the possibility of man-- of-- of undergoing some sort of a psychological mutation through which prejudice, bias is going to be obliterated.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really believed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is going to be the beginning of a new world, of a good world, where people can live side by side, being what they want to be without being afraid.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really believed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I will never again have that-- I was high, high on idealism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was just incredible that morning, just incredible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, then what happened, sure enough, as we found out later, the Russians did go into the camp and did rape.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even though the women said, [RUSSIAN], which in Russian means 'Jewish'-- I mean, that's what I heard, particularly one woman was raped.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's what I heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what happened to the four of us, the Frenchmen said, let's-- well, what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war was over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What do you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't even know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
